name: Your Numbers Report
description:
Have you ever wondered why your personality is a certain way? Or why others perceive you differently than you know yourself? Let me help you understand your true character by calculating the numbers from your name and birth date (a total of 6 numbers). This is a report written by me personally to explain your numbers. You will gain insight into your personality that you might not have observed or put into words. 

You must provide your full name that you use everyday, and your birth day, month, and year. You will receive your report as a pdf file. Your report will be sent by email within 48 hours depending on demand.

name: Fast Numbers Reading
description:
This is your chance to ask a question and receive an answer based on your 3 birth numbers. Do you have questions about career, love, life path, relocation, home energy? I'll answer your questions within 250 words. Please provide details, such as if you are asking about career, you need to tell me about yourself, what you're interested in, etc. You must provide your birth day, month, and year, along with your question. You will receive your answer by email.


Allow up to 48 hours for a response, depending on time availability. In the case that I can not answer your question based on numbers, I will refund your money.

name: Let's Talk Numbers
description:
Do you need someone to talk to? I offer objective advice based on numbers. If you've got a relationship issue, decisions to make (such as career, or relocation), and you want the guidance of numbers, let's talk!

After payment is made, I will email you to schedule a time with you. This service is only offered on Skype. You must be set up to be able to voice chat on Skype.

name: Relationship By Numbers Report
description:
Do you wonder about the compatibility you have with someone? I can help you understand the kind of relationship issues you may have with someone based on your numbers. With my personal report written for you, you will gain insight into what the other person is really like, and point out exactly where your conflicting issues could be. I provide strategic advice on how to handle negative situations, and tips on how to create a positive, loving relationship based on the needs of each person. 

For this report, I will need both persons' full name (that is used everyday), and both persons' birth day, month, and year. This report will be sent by email in pdf file within 48 hours, depending on demand.

name: Andrea's Numbers Kit for Feng Shui
description:
Placing numbers around your home or office can help you focus the energy to suit your needs. This kit includes 2 sets of digitally cut numbers (1 to 9) made from assorted printed card stock, and a quick reference guide for using numbers. Numbers are an easy way to promote positive Feng Shui. 

This item is delivered to you by letter post. 
Prints may vary from photo.
Price includes shipping worldwide.
Handmade in Canada.
